# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docker build context exclusions for the Oxy API image.
#
# Keep the context small and—critically—NEVER ship host build
# artifacts or secrets into an image layer:
#   - node_modules: reinstalled inside the image for linux/arm64
#     (native modules like sharp / @node-rs/argon2 must be built
#     for the target arch, not copied from the host).
#   - dist / lib / .turbo: rebuilt inside the image.
#   - .env*: live secrets must come from the runtime env, never
#     be baked into the image.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies (reinstalled per-arch inside the image)
**/node_modules
node_modules

# Build outputs (rebuilt inside the image)
**/dist
**/lib
**/build
**/.turbo
.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets & environment files — NEVER copy into an image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
dkim-private.pem
*_private.key
*_public.key

# Version control & CI
.git
.github
.gitignore
**/.gitignore

# Editor / OS noise
.vscode
.idea
**/*.swp
.DS_Store

# Tests, coverage, docs (not needed at runtime)
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/.eslintcache

# Other apps in the monorepo that the API image does not build.
# Keep their sources out of the image context, but allow package manifests so
# Docker can run a full-workspace frozen Bun install against the committed lock.
packages/accounts/*
!packages/accounts/package.json
packages/auth/*
!packages/auth/package.json
packages/auth-sdk/*
!packages/auth-sdk/package.json
packages/console/*
!packages/console/package.json
packages/inbox/*
!packages/inbox/package.json
packages/services/*
!packages/services/package.json
packages/test-app-expo/*
!packages/test-app-expo/package.json
packages/test-app-vite/*
!packages/test-app-vite/package.json

# Local Docker artifacts
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
